{"content": "I need to multiply 701\u2089 \u00d7 638\u2089.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n\n701\u2089 = 7\u00d79\u00b2 + 0\u00d79\u00b9 + 1\u00d79\u2070 = 7\u00d781 + 0\u00d79 + 1\u00d71 = 567 + 0 + 1 = 568\u2081\u2080\n\n638\u2089 = 6\u00d79\u00b2 + 3\u00d79\u00b9 + 8\u00d79\u2070 = 6\u00d781 + 3\u00d79 + 8\u00d71 = 486 + 27 + 8 = 521\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n\n568 \u00d7 521 = 295,928\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n\n295928 \u00f7 9 = 32880 r 8\n32880 \u00f7 9 = 3653 r 3\n3653 \u00f7 9 = 405 r 8\n405 \u00f7 9 = 45 r 0\n45 \u00f7 9 = 5 r 0\n5 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 5\n\nReading from bottom to top: 500838\u2089\n\n**Verification:**\n500838\u2089 = 5\u00d759049 + 0\u00d76561 + 0\u00d7729 + 8\u00d781 + 3\u00d79 + 8\u00d71 = 295245 + 0 + 0 + 648 + 27 + 8 = 295928\u2081\u2080 \u2713\n\n500838", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 1150, "completion_tokens": 410}